column1: #Spacecraft_Name: This column should be filled with the name of the spacecraft.
#Year: This column should be filled with the year in which the spacecraft was bought.
#Selling_Price: This column should be filled with the price the owner wants to sell the spacecraft at (in Bitcoins).
#Present_Price: This is the current ex-showroom price of the spacecraft (in Bitcoins).
#Kms_Driven: This is the distance completed by the spacecraft in Mm (mega meters).
#Seller_Type: Defines whether the seller is a dealer or an individual.
#Transmission: Defines whether the spacecraft is manual or automatic.
#Owner: Defines the number of owners the spacecraft has previously had.
